high_descs: Turn around and turn right towards the stove.
Grab the knife on the counter next to the toaster.
Turn right and face the bread on the counter to your right.
Slice the bread on the counter.
Turn right, then left, and left again around the counter and face the recycling bin on your right.
Place the knife inside of the recycling bin in front of you.
Turn around, then left, then right around the counter and face the bread on the counter to your right.
Take a slice of bread off of the counter.
Turn left and face the microwave on your left.
Heat up the bread in the microwave, take it out and close the microwave.
Turn left, then left again and face the blue recycling bin on your right.
Place the slice of bread in the recycling bin in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a hot slice of bread in the recycling bin.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the counter across from the stove.
Cut the bread on the counter.
Turn around and go to the recycling bin.
Put the knife in the recycling bin
Turn around and go to the counter across from the stove.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Cook the slice of bread in the microwave.
Turn around and go to the recycling bin.
Put the slice of bread in the recycling bin
anns.task_desc: Cook a slice of bread in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the door, then turn right and walk to the stove.
Pick up the knife on the left.
Turn right and walk to the end of the table and face the table.
Slice the loaf of bread on the table.
Turn right and follow the table to the sink, turn left and walk to the recycling bin and face it.
Drop the knife in the recycling bin.
Turn right and walk to the end of the table and turn right again until you get to the bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave and heat up the bread in the microwave.
Turn left and walk until the end of the table, then turn left and walk to the recycling bin.
Put the bread in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Warm up a slice of bread and put it in the recycling bin.

high_descs: Turn to your left then walk straight, turn left head to the toaster on the counter
Pick up the that is close to the stove
Turn to your right face the island counter
Slice the bread on top of the island counter
Turn to your right then left towards the sink, turn left the face the trash bin on your right
Drop the knife on the trash bin
Turn around to your right, head back to the island counter and face the bread
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter
Turn around to your left walk few steps and face the microwave
Open the microwave heat the bread inside, take it out and close the microwave
Turn to your left, then turn left again towards the stove then head to the trash bin
Drop the bread on the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Throw the knife and bread into the trash bin

high_descs: Turn and go to the toaster on the counter.
Pick up the knife that is to the left of the toaster.
Turn around  with the knife so you are facing the counter where the loaf of bread is.
With the knife slice the loaf of bread.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the trash can.
Put the knife in the trash can.
Turn and go to the loaf of bread that is on the counter.
Grab a slice of bread that is the closest to the edge of the counter.
Take the slice of bread and go to the microwave oven.
Open the microwave. Put the slice of bread inside the microwave on the left side in the front.  Close the door and start the microwave.  Open the door and grab the slice of bread.
With the bread in hand turn and go to the trash can in the corner.
Place the slice of bread in the trash can.
Turn and move to stand at the stove, facing the counter between the stove and toaster.
Pick up the sharp knife from the counter that's closest to the backsplash.
Turn and move to stand by the loaf of bread on the kitchen island while carrying the knife.
Slice half the loaf of bread.
Carry the knife to stand in front of the blue trash bin in the corner to the left of the counter.
Place the knife in the blue bin.
Turn and move back to the sliced loaf of bread on the kitchen island.
Pick up the end slice of bread from the counter.
Carry the bread to the microwave on the counter in the corner.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave, turn it on, and then remove once warmed.
Carry the slice of bread back across the kitchen to the blue trash bin in the corner.
Place the bread in the blue trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a warmed slice of bread.
